Pin Configuration:
Component	ESP32 Pin	 Connection Purpose
LED 1	   GPIO 18	        First LED output
LED 2	   GPIO 5	        Second LED output
LED 3	   GPIO 17	        Third LED output
Button 1	GPIO 32   	Mode cycle button
Button 2	GPIO 33	     Reset button
OLED SDA	GPIO 21  	I2C data line
OLED SCL	GPIO 22	    I2C clock line
OLED VCC	3.3V	     Power supply
OLED GND	GND	Ground


